short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Use omahaku.com on any website to add, rate and search

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Rate the current web page on omahaku.com. This extension is meant for the users of omahaku.com. It extends the standalone service by allowing you to edit the title and image of the omahaku.com item corresponding to the current page. In addition to managing your rating of the current web page, the full omahaku.com service is usable through the extension, including personalized searches.
